  => "  iter-49 14-topo measured (excl cartoon outlier):"
  => "    Σ = 79 + 141 + 145 + 146 + 169 + 180 + 196 + 203 +"
  => "        229 + 303 + 434 + 463 + 478 + 604 = 3770"
  => "    Mean (n=14) = 269.3"
  => "  iter-36 reference 15-topo (excl cartoon, from 16-topo mean=299):"
