  => "    Cartoon contribution = 741 (iter-48 measurement)"
  => "    15-topo Σ (excl cartoon) = 4784 - 741 = 4043"
  => "    Mean = 4043 / 15 = 269.5"
  => "  ★ Match: 269.3 vs 269.5 = 99.93% — VIRTUALLY IDENTICAL ★"

@R clay-iter-49-cartoon-source-of-iter-36-mean-inflation :: meta [4]
  => "Cartoon outlier CAUSAL ANALYSIS:"
  => "  iter-36 reported D=3 mean = 299"
  => "  iter-49 14-topo (excl cartoon) mean = 269"
  => "  Difference = 30 units (10% of iter-36 mean)"
  => "  Cartoon contributes (741-269)/16 ≈ 30 units to 16-topo mean"
  => "  → cartoon SOLELY responsible for ~10% upward bias in iter-36"
  => "  Without cartoon, iter-49 14-topo identical to iter-36 reference"
  => "  Cartoon = iter-38 predicted outlier ('non-physical random hops')"
  => "  Conclusion: iter-36 measurement was systematically correct,"
  => "              and cartoon should be excluded from D=3 baseline"

